nodes.title: Set Last Layer   &  Flux Guidance
widgets_values:
-------------------- Rescale CFG ------------------
( def: 0.7 ) * (<) less adherence, softer, smoother
             * (>) more adherence, crisper detail
------------------- Flux Guidance -----------------
( def: 3.5 ) * (<-3) more organic/creative outputs
             * (5–>) stricter prompt binding

nodes.title: Model Shift
widgets_values:
----------------- Model base shift ----------------
( def: 0.5 )
----------------- Model max shift -----------------
( def: 1.15 )
         * lower smoother less hallucination.
         * higher more detail, possible noise/grit.

nodes.title: LoRA's Hooks
widgets_values:
- Hooks timeline: start with original Model strength, then Strength 1, then 2.
- Flow: base weights first; at 'Str 1 start' apply S1; at 'Str 2 start' apply S2.
- Strength 1 and Strength 2 are PERCENTAGES of the current Model strength.
- Example: Model=1.20, S1=80% → effective=0.96; S2=120% → effective=1.44.
* To disable hooks via timing: set 'Strength 1/2 start at %' to 100 for both.
* To disable via levels: set 'Strength 1' and 'Strength 2' sliders to 100%.
